videos.description: Texas Tech's Keenan Evans makes a great steal and lobs it up to Zach Smith for the dunk.
videos.headline: Red Raiders throw down alley-oop jam

videos.description: Norense Odiase makes great use of the backboard and sets up Zhaire Smith for the dunk.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Smith throws it down

videos.description: Wildcats' Scottie Lindsey heaves the ball to hit the buzzer-beater, ending the first half.
videos.headline: Northwestern's Lindsey hits half-court buzzer-beater

videos.description: Texas Tech's Zach Smith draws a foul when going in for a layup, and the ball swirls around the rim and goes in.
videos.headline: Red Raiders' Smith scores with nice driving layup

videos.description: Davide Moretti drains 3-point jumper from the wing.
videos.headline: Red Raiders' Moretti sinks 3-point jumper
